Morrow talked to him.
Didn't you?

24
00:03:04.667 --> 00:03:09.042
Mr. Teng won't be a problem unless
he wants to work 65 years for no pay.

25
00:03:09.125 --> 00:03:12.458
Ooh. Teng.

26
00:03:12.542 --> 00:03:13.542
Stingy.

27
