481
00:44:39.125 --> 00:44:40.583
So you want to help him?

482
00:44:42.208 --> 00:44:43.792
Look at her face.

483
00:44:44.542 --> 00:44:45.542
Her body language.

484
00:44:45.625 --> 00:44:48.042
I mean. if I didn't know better.
